Fordo Motor Co say e dey consolidate for di Indomite side under one new organisation wey go dey headed by W. Wayne Booker.

For di whole Asia Pacific, dem go do Ford subsidiary for Japan, Australia, Taiwan, New Zealand, and dem go dey work with Ford business associate for di whole region.

Dem dey do dis one for Melbourne, Australia, and for Ford headquarter wey dey Dearborn, Michael.

Mr. Booker, di executive of Ford's Latin America Automobile Operations since December 1988, na im dem dey call di vice president of Ford Asia-Pacific.

